{"tid":893203,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【銀主走貨】九龍塘1,400呎豪宅蝕600萬開拍","createTime":"2018-11-07T12:32:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-07T16:20:18.000Z","uid":174649,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2650e7ecf487403561dc7a0e7f2367d365f4998e","tid":893203,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T12:32:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181107/large/1541592758_fc57.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181107%2Flarge%2F1541592758_fc57.jpg&h=4a0086fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n樓市轉差，銀行軟化，銀主盤陸續減價求售。繼尖沙嘴港景峯後，嘉里(683)發展的九龍塘豪宅義德道1及3號首間銀主盤亦減價拍賣。<br />\n<br />\n義德道1及3號銀主盤為2座低層B室，實用面積1,409方呎，三房間隔，上月曾開價5,200萬元連一個車位拍賣，但無人問津，銀主安排本月20日由環亞翻拍，開價降低220萬至4,980萬元，較業主2016年6月連車位買入價5,582.2萬元低602.2萬元或10%，若以底價成交，恐成為項目「第一滴血」。"},{"pid":"6d9273f9292bb7703d8d8f97fa5f73810e557cf3","tid":893203,"uid":3167,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T12:59:09.000Z","msg":"五千萬嘅樓唔係港豬住唔計"},{"pid":"9a06fe0e6687b5643fe2a6775bf95160a1a70dbf","tid":893203,"uid":997,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T13:02:46.000Z","msg":"有人接先有第一口價既 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8513e3b685bb79ef1fd508c51fac2f95c73411a0","tid":893203,"uid":37460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a06fe0e6687b5643fe2a6775bf95160a1a70dbf","tid":893203,"uid":997,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T13:02:46.000Z","msg":"有人接先有第一口價既 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T13:08:25.000Z","msg":"五千萬景 對住個 金色喇叭人, 睇見都唔開胃."},{"pid":"5947d24427cb53cb2943ff206eb3ac19c3e1638d","tid":893203,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8513e3b685bb79ef1fd508c51fac2f95c73411a0","tid":893203,"uid":37460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a06fe0e6687b5643fe2a6775bf95160